Don't colonize in darkness, which slows down colonization and delays pinning.&amp;nbsp; Expose to normal low-level ambient light on a day/night schedule from day of inoculation.&lt;br /&gt;RR</content>\n<name>RogerRabbit</name>\n<next>16951044</next>\n<prev>16949525</prev>\n<first>16948519</first>\n<last>16954650</last>\n<when>1349177643</when>\n<utime>10/02/12 02:34 PM</utime>\n</post>"}